    image = random.choice(image_src)
    with open(image, "rb") as f:
        return Response(200, Headers.from_ext(image.suffix), [f.read()])

# /é‡å®šå‘åˆ°/image
root.redirect(301, "/", "/image/")
```

## ä½¿ç”¨å­ç›®å½•

```python
